aa(lp11
VWell, I have had a great blessing as a former president,
p12
aVbecause I have had an access
p13
aVthat very few other people in the world have ever had
p14
aVto get to know so many people around this whole universe.
p15
aVNot only am I familiar with the 50 states in the United States,
p16
