aa(lp22
VSo our overall commitment at the Carter Center
p23
aVis to promote human rights,
p24
aVand knowing the world as I do, I can tell you without any equivocation
p25
aVthat the number one abuse of human rights on Earth
p26
aVis, strangely, not addressed quite often, is the abuse of women and girls.
p27
aa(lp28
V(Applause)
