aVand so 89 universities in America are now condemned
p201
aVby the Department of Education under Title IX
p202
aVbecause the officials of the universities are not taking care of the women
p203
aVto protect them from sexual assault.
p204
aVThe Department of Justice says that more than half of the rapes
p205
aVon a college campus take place by serial rapists,
p206
aVbecause outside of the university system,
p207
aVif they rape somebody, they'll be prosecuted,
p208
aVbut when they get on a university campus, they can rape with impunity.
p209
aVThey're not prosecuted.
p210
aVThose are the kinds of things that go on in our society.
