aa(lp212
VAnother thing that's very serious about the abuse of women and girls
p213
aVis the lack of equal pay for equal work,
p214
aVas you know. (Applause)
p215
aVAnd this is sometimes misinterpreted, but for full-time employment,
p216
aVa woman in the United States now gets 23 percent less than a man.
p217
