aa(lp232
VAnother problem with the United States
p233
aVis we are the most warlike nation on Earth.
p234
aVWe have been to war with about 25 different countries
p235
aVsince the Second World War.
p236
aVSometimes, we've had soldiers on the ground fighting.
p237
aVThe other times, we've been flying overhead
p238
aVdropping bombs on people.
p239
aVOther times, of course, now, we have drones that attack people and so forth.
p240
aVWe've been at war with 25 different countries
p241
aVor more since the Second World War.
p242
aVThere was four years, I won't say which ones,
p243
aVwhere we didn't \u2014
p244
aV(Applause) \u2014 we didn't drop a bomb, we didn't launch a missile,
p245
aVwe didn't fire a bullet.
p246
aVBut anyway, those kinds of things, the resort to violence
p247
aVand the misinterpretation of the holy scriptures
p248
aVare what causes, are the basic causes, of abuse of women and girls.
