aa(lp250
VThere's one more basic cause that I need not mention,
p251
aVand that is that in general, men don't give a damn.
p252
aV(Applause) That's true.
p253
aVThe average man that might say, I'm against the abuse of women and girls
p254
aVquietly accepts the privileged position that we occupy,
p255
aVand this is very similar to what I knew when I was a child,
p256
aVwhen separate but equal had existed.
p257
aVRacial discrimination, legally, had existed for 100 years,
p258
aVfrom 1865 at the end of the War Between the States, the Civil War,
p259
